#

Classic Ukrainian Borscht

90 min
$10
180 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Ukrainian

Course:

Main CourseSoup

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodHealthy

Description

A hearty and vibrant beet soup, rich in flavors and nutrients, perfect for warming up on a chilly day.

Ingredients

  • beets: 3 medium
  • cabbage: 2 cups, chopped
  • carrot: 1, grated
  • onion: 1, diced
  • potato: 2, diced
  • tomato paste: 2 tablespoons
  • vegetable broth: 6 cups
  • garlic: 3 cloves, minced
  • bay leaf: 1
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • dill: for garnish
  • sour cream: for serving
